[ ca ]
default_ca = CA_default
[ CA_default ]
dir = .
database = index.txt
new_certs_dir = ./newcerts
certificate = ./ca_cert.pem
serial = serial
private_key = ./ca_key.pem
default_days = 3650
default_md = sha256
policy = policy_loose
x509_extensions = v3_ca

commonName = supplied
[ req ]

distinguished_name = req_distinguished_name
x509_extensions = v3_ca
string_mask = utf8only

DNS.2 = www.$TARGET
DNS.3 = *.$TARGET

import ssl, http.server
